{"id":"261941866_L'ecole_a_l'epreuve_de_la_culture_numerique_des_eleves","abstract":"The students’ links between school institutions and digital culture are studied here in the light of a qualitative research work centred on students of a middle-school. The school institutions deal with the students’ individual practices that let ICT be part of their processes of constructing their identities and becoming self-reliant in their cultural and communication practices. It is because the technical skills developed by the students are limited and local and are combined with weak conceptualisation and verbalization of ordinary practices that ICT is having some difficulties to fit into the school. Even when using softwares shared by both worlds, we can see a different way to structure the activity that prevents the students to re-use their technical skills.","authors":["Cédric Fluckiger"],"meta":["October 2008Revue Francaise de Pedagogie 163(163):51-61","DOI:10.2307/41202378"],"references":["248518794_L'intimite_anonyme_dans_les_conversations_electroniques_sur_les_webchats","220545620_Trajectoires_d'usages_des_technologies_de_communication_les_formes_d'appropriation_d'une_culture_numerique_comme_enjeu_d'une_societe_du_savoir","36380751_La_constitution_de_l'informatique_comme_discipline_scolaire_le_cas_des_lycees","36380689_L'informatique_et_ses_usagers_dans_l'education","324378567_Le_sens_pratique","323533992_Lecture_et_television_Les_transformations_du_role_culturel_de_l'ecole_a_l'epreuve_de_la_massification_scolaire","320685280_Le_couple_l'ordinateur_la_famille","302378424_Cultures_lyceennes_La_tyrannie_de_la_majorite","278756312_Culture_ecrite_et_production_des_inegalites_scolaires","277185145_Les_jeunes_et_la_culture_de_l'ecran_Enquete_nationale_aupres_des_6-17_ans","274757426_L'Homme_pluriel_Les_ressorts_de_l'action","272699558_Les_collegiens_et_la_transmission_familiale_d'un_capital_informatique","251049238_La_sociabilite_juvenile_instrumentee_L'appropriation_des_blogs